<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q12_v1" title="Q12_v1" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>Boleta de pago de Carla (mes de junio):<br />
- Sueldo bruto: $<m:math><m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn></m:math><br />
- Descuento por salud: <m:math><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math> del sueldo bruto<br />
- Otros descuentos fijos: $5 000<br /><br />
¿Cuál es el monto descontado por salud?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">$1 440<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El descuento por salud es el <m:math><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math> de <m:math><m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>, y <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,18</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>14&#160;400</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Por lo tanto, $1 440 no corresponde al monto descontado por salud.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">$14 400<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! El descuento por salud es el <m:math><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math> del sueldo bruto: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,18</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>14&#160;400</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Por lo tanto, el monto descontado por salud es $14 400.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">$94 400<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El <m:math><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math> de <m:math><m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,18</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>14&#160;400</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Además, 94 400 es mayor que el sueldo bruto de 80 000, así que no puede ser solo el descuento por salud.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">$40 000<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El descuento por salud es el <m:math><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math> de <m:math><m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>, y <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,18</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>14&#160;400</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. En cambio, 40 000 corresponde al <m:math><m:mn>50</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math> de <m:math><m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>, no al <m:math><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Identificar lo que se pide</strong></p>
            <p>Se pregunta solo por el monto descontado por salud. No se pide el sueldo líquido ni el total de descuentos.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Reconocer el dato relevante</strong></p>
            <p>El sueldo bruto es $80 000 y el descuento por salud corresponde al 18% de ese sueldo.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Calcular el 18% de 80 000</strong></p>
            <p>Convertimos 18% a decimal:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>18</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>%</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mfrac>
                    <m:mn>18</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>100</m:mn>
                  </m:mfrac>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>0,18</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Luego multiplicamos:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>0,18</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>×</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>14&#160;400</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Verificar</strong></p>
            <p>El descuento por salud es $14 400. Los otros descuentos fijos de $5 000 no se usan para responder esta pregunta, porque no forman parte del descuento por salud.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es la <strong>B</strong>: $14 400.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>